---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Phone Stand for Desk 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of adjustable phone holders. Keep your second screen visible while working.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} articleSchema={{headline: pageTitle, description: pageDescription, datePublished: '2026-05', authorName: 'Toolwise Team'}} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Phone Stand for Desk</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · 270-Degree Adjustment</div>

      <p>Keeping your phone visible while working helps you stay connected without picking it up constantly. After testing multiple phone stands, one stands out for its stability, adjustability, and thoughtful design that works with any phone or tablet.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Lamicall Adjustable Phone Stand</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>270-degree angle adjustment</strong> — find your perfect viewing angle</li>
          <li><strong>Stable base supports tablets up to 10 inches</strong> — works with any device</li>
          <li><strong>Rubber pads protect phone from scratches</strong> — secure grip</li>
          <li><strong>15mm hook width fits cases</strong> — no need to remove phone case</li>
          <li><strong>Hollow design allows charging cable through</strong> — charge while displayed</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=phone+stand+desk&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most phone stands either wobble or don't adjust enough. The Lamicall offers 270-degree rotation with a stable weighted base that doesn't tip over. The hollow design lets you charge your phone while it's displayed, and the wide hook accommodates most phone cases.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Anyone who wants to keep their phone visible at their desk. It's perfect for video calls, monitoring notifications, following recipes, or using your phone as a second screen while working.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>